            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-182] zookeeper_init accepts empty host-port string and returns valid pointer to zhandle_t.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-182</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Please, add this test to src/c/tests/TestZookeeperInit.cc to reproduce this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    void testEmptyAddressString()&lt;/p&gt;
    {
        zh=zookeeper_init(&quot;&quot;,0,0,0,0,0);
        CPPUNIT_ASSERT(zh==0);
    }</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Linux&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
